    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Six months ago we completed
a &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://www.rockethub.com/projects/6066-into-the-green-green-mud-multimedia-novel"&gt;RocketHub campaign&lt;/a&gt;
with your help.
Since then
we&amp;#8217;ve been editing,
sketching,
adjusting,
coding,
testing,
designing,
and coding some&amp;nbsp;more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;#8217;m happy to say
we&amp;#8217;ve reached a milestone.
The &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/oddbird/greenmud/"&gt;foundation is complete&lt;/a&gt;,
the &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://greengreenmud.com/"&gt;frontmatter is styled&lt;/a&gt;,
and from here on out we are working
page by page and chapter by chapter
to bring everything&amp;nbsp;together.&lt;/p&gt;
